<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEW AND USEFUL: CONSUMERS; 
</P>
<P>
A BRIGHT DEVICE TO AID CHILDREN AND INVALIDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LYNN SIMROSS 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Extend-A-Switch is a simple and inexpensive way to make light switches 
accessible to small children or people confined to wheelchairs. 
</P>
<P>
Extend-A-Switch has no cords or pulleys that can knot or tangle. It is a 
13-inch strip of plastic with a slot at the top that hooks over the switch. The 
device, at $1.99, is available at Gerald's Ace Hardware in Westchester or from 
3-V Co., P.O. Box 3312, El Segundo, Calif. 90245. One is $1.99; two, $3.75, 
plus 90 cents shipping and handling. 
</P>
<P>
For Bed 'n' Beach, or Merely a Cover-Up 
</P>
<P>
Cool Cat is a furniture cover-up that also can double as a beach towel. 
</P>
<P>
The 35x60-inch heavy terry cloth towel can be used to cover sofas, chairs or 
the end of a bed to keep them free of cat hairs or deter scratching. Or, you 
can take the towel -- which has a cat design -- to the pool or the beach. 
</P>
<P>
Rabbit Foot Inc.recently added its Cool Cat line, which includes T-shirts, 
sweat shirts and nightshirts. 
</P>
<P>
The suggested retail price is about $22.95. In the Los Angeles area the towel 
is available at Cats Plus in Burbank, Chatsworth Pet Center, Woodcliff Animal 
Hospital in Chatsworth, Four Paws Only in Toluca Lake, The Cat's Meow in 
Orange, Dr. Roe's Pet Headquarters in Malibu and (no kidding) It's A Dog's Life 
in Studio City. 
</P>
<P>
You can order it, for $22.95, including shipping and handling (California 
residents add 6.75% sales tax), from Rabbit Foot Inc., 20945 Devonshire St., 
Suite 102, Chatsworth, Calif. 91311. In California, call (818) 700-6955; 
outside California, (800) 228-6902. 
</P>
<P>
A Hinge Helper for a Do-It-Yourselfer 
</P>
<P>
Do-it-yourselfers may want to consider a California company's latest invention, 
the Hinge Recess-Matic, a device that helps you cut hinge recesses on doors and 
woodwork quickly and accurately. 
</P>
<P>
The cutting tool, introduced by Seto Products in Pasadena, fits any hand-held 
power drill and has three adjustments to accommodate various door thicknesses, 
as well as an adapter for 3 1/2-inch and 4-inch hinge sizes. 
</P>
<P>
The suggested retail price is $29.95, and in Southern California it's available 
at All-American Home Center and in most Lumber City and Barr Lumber stores. You 
can order it for $29.95, including shipping and handling, from Seto Products, 
3165 E. Green St., Pasadena, Calif. 91107; (213) 259-3356. 
</P>
</TEXT>
