<SUBJECT>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; CALIFORNIA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICALS; 
LEGISLATORS -- ORANGE COUNTY; CALIFORNIA STATE SENATE; HILL, FRANK; GRAHAM, 
JANICE LYNN; LEWIS, ROBERT 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
