Tharp Works Moving to Chicago: Hubbard Street Dance Company will announce "a 
major artistic collaboration" with choreographer Twyla Tharp at a press 
conference this morning at the company's headquarters in Chicago. Sources close 
to the company report that the announcement will involve Hubbard Street's 
acquisition of modern-dance works that Tharp created in the 1970s for her own 
