<P>
Profile; Main Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
ARTISTS; ART EXHIBITS; PAINTINGS; SCULPTURE; VIDEO RECORDIGS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
